<section
    class="contact-section w-full min-h-[30vh] md:min-h-[60vh] py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-8 bg-[#141414] flex items-center justify-center"
>
    <div
        class="w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center text-center md:-translate-x-5"
    >
        <h2
            class="contact-title text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-white tracking-tight"
        >
            Un projet ? <span class="text-[#5C8F3A]">Parlons-en</span> !
        </h2>

        <p
            class="contact-subtitle text-base sm:text-lg md:text-2xl text-[#B8B8B8] mb-8 md:mb-12 font-medium max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl px-4 md:px-0"
        >
            Nous sommes à votre écoute pour concrétiser vos idées et propulser
            votre business.
        </p>

        <a
            href="/contact"
            class="contact-cta mx-auto group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 sm:px-12 md:px-16 py-3 md:py-4 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-[#E07A1F] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#C86618] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(224,122,31,0.4)] whitespace-nowrap no-underline"
        >
            <span
                class="relative text-white font-medium text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase transition-colors"
            >
                Nous contacter
            </span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
